md:
giải nghĩa từ "ago" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

ago (adverb)

* Meaning: in the past; a period of time before the present
* Example: I graduated from college three years ago.
* Related words: before, previously, earlier, in the past

ago (noun)

* Meaning: a period of time in the past
* Example: The incident happened a week ago.
* Related words: past, history, earlier, previously

Note: The meaning of "ago" can vary depending on the context in which it is used. In general, it refers to a period of time in the past, but it can also be used to indicate a specific point in the past.
